No. 10-757. Michael Newdow, et al., Petitioners v. John G. Roberts, Jr., Chief Justice of the United States, et al. 563 U.S. 1001, 131 S. Ct. 2441,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1235,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3573. May 16, 2011.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 390 U.S. App. D.C. 273, 603 F.3d 1002.
